  "title": "使用数据业务上网经常掉线，如何解决？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  请在移动网络信号较强的地方上网。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  在**设置**界面，点击**移动网络**，勾选**始终连接数据业务**复选框。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171457886001.gif)</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"> </p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  向网络运营商咨询手机的接入点名称（APN）参数是否正确。在**移动网络**中，点击**接入点名称（****APN****）**，可以查看当前使用的接入点。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171457398002.gif)</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  若尝试以上方法后仍然不能解决问题，请备份重要数据，将手机恢复出厂设置，重新连接。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"> </p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171457837003.gif)</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"> </p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  禁止应用程序通过移动网络上网。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">在**设置**界面，点击**联网应用**，选择要限制上网权限的应用程序，点击对应的![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171457248004.gif)。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171457691005.gif)</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"> </p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  如无必要，请关闭后台数据同步。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">打开通知面板，选择![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171457120006.gif)，然后点击![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171458769007.gif)。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171458774008.jpg)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171458272009.gif)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171458487010.jpg)</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"> </p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  退出不使用的应用程序。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">长按![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171458997011.gif)打开最近使用的应用程序列表，滑动列表或点击![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171458293012.gif)关闭应用程序，也可以点击![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171459994013.gif)关闭所有应用程序。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"> </p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</p>",
